# {{WORKSPACE_NAME}} — Tasks

Shared task tracker for the **{{WORKSPACE_NAME}}** workspace.

This repository sits at the workspace-parent level, alongside the meta-repo,
package repos, and project repos. It is its own git repository so that task
history can be versioned and synced independently of the source code.

## Layout

```
Tasks/
├── TODO/    # planned tasks, not yet started
├── ACTIVE/  # tasks currently in progress
└── DONE/    # completed tasks (archive)
```

## Conventions

- One task per Markdown file. Name pattern: `<date>-<short-slug>.md`
  (e.g. `2026-05-14-add-rate-limiter.md`).
- Move files between `TODO/` → `ACTIVE/` → `DONE/` as state changes;
  do not duplicate.
- Cross-link related code in the corresponding package or project repo using
  relative paths from this repo's root (`../packages/<name>/...` or
  `../<project-repo>/...`).
